data.description: Nestled on a spacious acre lot, this immaculate residence boasts a unique design with tons of natural light, and more than enough space for all your needs. The inviting living room with its cozy fireplace is perfect for relaxing evenings. The stylish kitchen and dining area create a great space for entertaining friends and family. Just off the kitchen is an enormous great room waiting for large gatherings.  Spacious, sun splashed bedrooms keep everyone happy with 3 of the 4 boasting their own private baths.  The master suite is a dream with soaring ceilings, specialty tub, and shower. Enjoy the beauty of nature in your own backyard! The property features a large, fenced yard with mature trees, and a fantastic patio for outdoor gatherings, BBQs, and al fresco dining. Conveniently located, this property offers easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and all the amenities. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your new home.
